When viewing Agile board, issue keys on cards are showing at elipses instead of the actual issue key.

This occurs when the first swimlane is collapsed. Uncollapsing the first swimlane will fix the problem.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *JIRA Software Cloud*. Using *JIRA Software Server*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSWSERVER-11384].
  {panel}

If you have an estimated issue included in a version and a sprint, then remove it from a version at a later time, the sprint original estimate no longer includes the removed issue, despite it was included in the original estimate at the time that sprint was done.
